data.description: Do not miss this fantastic 3 bedroom, 3 bath townhome conveniently located off Winnetka Ave in New Hope. With new carpet, countertops, kitchen sink, lighting, and paint, this home is move-in ready. The main level features beautiful LVP flooring, a cozy gas fireplace in the living room open kitchen & dining room, as well as a powder bath & laundry. Upstairs you will find 3 spacious bedrooms, two of which have their own bathroom & walk-in closets. The primary bedroom has a fantastic sitting area that would be perfect for a home office or additional area for watching TV and relaxing. You will find that you are close to everything including parks, shopping & restaurants. This home is available for quick close and is ready for you. Welcome home!
